1
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:14,440
What you call a crime

2
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:16,200
in our eyes

3
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:18,040
is righteous revenge.

4
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:20,360
'We.'

5
00:00:22,120 --> 00:00:23,050
You admitted it.

6
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:28,200
That's right.

7
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,800
We are a team.

8
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:32,680
Anyway, we've achieved our goal.

9
00:00:33,040 --> 00:00:35,300
Lu Yuanzhou and Zhang Song are both dead,

10
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:37,520
and Zhou Zheng is half-dead.

11
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:39,160
Ultimately,

12
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:41,040
we won.

13
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:44,920
Zhao Wen.

14
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:47,810
Wang Yuanyuan has already confessed.

15
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:49,300
For you to keep holding out

16
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:50,680
is pointless.

17
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,200
I know.

18
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:55,440
You went to the hospital to take Zhou Zheng away

19
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:57,680
to fulfill the promise between you two.

20
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:58,680
Right?

21
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:07,000
Right.

22
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:13,490
I messed everything up.

23
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:17,560
Even if Zhou Zheng becomes a vegetable,

24
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,900
Xiaoling still can't escape.

25
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:24,039
She might be forced by the Zhou family

26
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:26,370
to take care of him for the rest of her life.

27
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,380
She has suffered too much.

28
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,780
You remember Zhao Wen, right?

29
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:38,580
She has a daughter.

30
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:39,850
She's seven.

31
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:42,490
She joined your plan in the first place

32
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,560
because of her daughter.

33
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,460
But what about now?

34
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,960
To help you,

35
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:51,680
she doesn't even care about her daughter anymore.

36
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,440
Those men all deserve to die.

37
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,400
Especially Lu Yuanzhou.

38
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,440
That pervert.

39
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:13,960
Ah.

40
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:15,160
Will she

41
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,360
be

42
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,600
like a dead fish?

43
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,320
Ah.

44
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,040
Is this okay?

45
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,440
Does it feel good?

46
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,820
Ah, does it feel great?

47
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,440
Sigh.

48
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:32,500
Actually, you knew early on that Lu Yuanzhou

49
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:35,600
liked to take women to the construction site's rooftop.

50
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,720
So that night,

51
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,520
you deliberately called him

52
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,980
just to lure him to the edge of the rooftop

53
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,100
so that Qi Xiaoling

54
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,700
could carry out your plan.

55
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,660
Those two have confessed.

56
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,330
Qi Xiaoling.

57
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,440
Wang Yuanyuan and Zhao Wen have confessed.

58
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,480
We now focus on

59
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,400
evidence rather than confessions.

60
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,520
Even if you don't confess,

61
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,840
the existing evidence is enough to convict you.

62
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,500
So there's no need to hold out.

63
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,160
Confessing early

64
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:19,010
is good for all three of you.

65
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,600
What else do you want to know?

66
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,260
Who is the mastermind?

67
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,250
Qi Xiaoling,

68
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,360
you should know

69
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,800
that the sentencing for the principal offender

70
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,060
and the accomplice is vastly different.

71
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,650
There is no principal or accomplice among us.

72
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,120
Then there must be

73
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,000
someone behind you

74
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,090
connecting you all.

75
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,200
No one connected us.

76
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,400
It's fate.

77
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,600
We are three miserable women.

78
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,380
Then why did you leave paper brides at the scene?

79
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:01,400
That was my idea.

80
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,920
Domestic violence is a very hidden form of violence.

81
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,360
I believe besides us three,

82
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:09,490
there are many women suffering from domestic violence.

83
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,580
They can't escape,

84
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:12,900
nor can they get a divorce.

85
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,060
Many choose to remain silent.

86
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,500
But I just wanted to speak up for them.

87
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,040
I want domestic violence

88
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:21,040
to get more attention from society.

89
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,080
The three murders

90
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,610
were also planned by you together.

91
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:29,360
Yes.

92
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:33,300
How exactly did you plan them?

93
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,900
Based on the characteristics

94
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:38,400
and usual habits of those three men.

95
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:41,400
What?

96
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:44,890
Do you police think we can't plan them?

97
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:47,170
Did you refer to any past cases,

98
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,120
such as the Scavenger case from ten years ago?

99
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:50,650
Qiu Chen.

100
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,800
Come out for a moment.

101
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:08,440
Who allowed you to ask about the Scavenger?

102
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,360
I was about to get key information.

103
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,440
When you hold a hammer,

104
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:13,040
everything looks like a nail.

105
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,040
But her MO...

106
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:16,040
I'm telling you, the Scavenger case is already closed.

107
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,200
If you ask this kind of leading question again,

108
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:20,200
stay out of the interrogation room.

109
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,320
Look at your state right now.

110
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,840
Even Qi Xiaoling is calmer than you.

111
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,770
Understood.

112
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:38,770
Qi Xiaoling.

113
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:43,240
Tell us the details of how you committed the crime.

114
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,240
It's very simple.

115
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,659
We just exploited their weaknesses.

116
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:49,620
Zhao Wen said Zhou Zheng deserved to die.

117
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,770
Why did she say that?

118
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,100
These hands of mine

119
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,250
weren't always this rough.

120
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,640
They used to paint and play the piano.

121
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:04,130
But ever since I met that man...

122
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:06,400
The feng shui in our neighborhood is exceptionally good.

123
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,400
And I can assure you that within three years,

124
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,260
the prices will definitely go up.

125
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,040
Xiaoling,

126
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,240
will you

127
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,520
marry me?

128
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,000
Not long after we got married,

129
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:22,560
I realized

130
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:25,360
that Zhou Zheng was an absolute violent maniac

131
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,490
and a control freak.

132
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,300
He was suspicious of every man around me.

133
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,659
What are you doing?

134
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:38,240
Who was that guy you were acting all lovey-dovey with just now?

135
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,640
That was my colleague.

136
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,120
We're...

137
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,850
Colleagues.

138
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,360
Colleagues are that intimate?

139
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:43,640
Ah!

140
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:53,200
The Zhou family said you had an affair with someone named Zhang Kai.

141
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,530
How do you explain that?

142
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,240
That's my ex-boyfriend.

143
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:59,440
We haven't contacted each other in a long time.

144
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,200
I don't know why he

145
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,520
sent me a message that day,

146
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,380
and Zhou Zheng happened to see it.

147
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:07,600
Then he went crazy and said I cheated on him,

148
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,620
threatening me with suicide.

149
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,200
Can you believe me?

150
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,240
I really didn't.

151
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:13,770
I didn't.

152
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,120
If you act like this again,

153
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,840
I'll kill myself.

154
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,600
Zhou Zheng, don't.

155
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,160
Zhou Zheng, I... I'll listen to you.

156
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,120
I'll do whatever you say.

157
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:19,920
Zhou Zheng, what are you doing?

158
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,120
Ah!

159
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,240
If you hook up with another man again,

160
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,160
I'll jump from here.

161
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:22,560
No, no, no.

162
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:22,960
No, no, no.

163
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,240
I can't. I can't.

164
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,520
Come down, please.

165
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:25,880
Don't, don't, don't.

166
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,120
Calm down. Calm down.

167
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,980
How can I calm down?

168
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:29,600
Ah.

169
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,620
Please.

170
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:30,900
I...

171
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:32,640
I was wrong.

172
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,800
It was my fault, okay?

173
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,640
At first, I thought he was really going to kill himself.

174
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,720
I was terrified.

175
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,640
Later, I realized

176
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,760
he was just acting.

177
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,640
He has a histrionic personality.

178
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:48,120
He likes to play the role of

179
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,800
a deeply affectionate person,

180
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,120
a perfect husband,

181
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,200
or even a pitiful victim.

182
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,920
Besides controlling me,

183
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,240
he also spread rumors everywhere,

184
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,800
painting me as

185
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,840
an absolute slut.

186
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,960
Officer.

187
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:07,200
Don't you think he deserves to die?

188
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,120
Understood.

189
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,300
You can't understand.

190
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:20,760
Only those who have truly experienced it can understand.

191
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,280
The plan begins.

192
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:45,960
I replaced Zhou Zheng's rope as planned.

193
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:57,250
I have prepared everything on Zhang Song's side.

194
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:59,640
Leave Lu Yuanzhou to me.

195
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:11,520
Hello?

196
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,040
Lu Yuanzhou.

197
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,010
You're playing quite wild.

198
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,260
Had enough fun?

199
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,770
Let's settle our score.

200
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,160
Where are you?

201
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,420
I'm right across from you.

202
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,000
Come on.

203
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,480
You've all worked hard.

204
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,040
Cheers.

205
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,000
Yeah.

206
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:01,800
What are you drinking?

207
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:02,400
Let me see.

208
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,530
Don't fall in again.

209
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,160
Red dates and longans.

210
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,760
Haha, very healthy.

211
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,600
Add some goji berries later,

212
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,600
and have him serve it to Chief Zhang.

213
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,400
Hey, Master,

214
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:15,080
let's not mention Chief Zhang.

215
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,960
This case is finally closed.

216
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,160
Let's have a good meal

217
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,160
today.

218
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:20,320
Yeah.

219
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,200
It's not over.

220
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:25,080
There should be one more person.

221
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:27,000
How can you be sure

222
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:29,400
there's someone behind the three of them?

223
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:30,800
Intuition.

224
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,370
What do you mean?

225
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:33,960
Intuition.

226
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:38,600
My intuition tells me your intuition is wrong.

227
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:40,560
This case is clearly closed,

228
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,600
but you're just looking for trouble.

229
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,930
Alright, stop talking.

230
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,920
Today is just for a happy meal,

231
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,400
let's not talk about work.

232
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:47,730
Yeah.

233
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,720
Oh, don't mention it.

234
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,280
Nowadays, getting married

235
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:54,340
not only costs money, but also lives.

236
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,480
I'm a little afraid of marriage now.

237
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:57,960
What's scary isn't marriage,

238
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:58,890
it's the person.

239
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:01,720
Find the right person and you'll be fine.

240
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,320
Hey, Siyu,

241
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,780
I highly recommend

242
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,920
if you're looking for your other half,

243
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:06,600
you can look within our police force.

244
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,000
Right?

245
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:07,960
Police...

246
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:09,290
What?

247
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,240
Recommending yourself?

248
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,280
Don't you think these cases

249
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:14,880
look familiar?

250
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:19,240
You mean

251
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,400
the Scavenger case from ten years ago?

252
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:21,930
Exactly.

253
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,360
Normally,

254
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:27,660
these three women should hide their relationship.

255
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,360
But the paper bride at the crime scenes

256
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:31,560
directly connected these three cases.

257
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,260
Why do you think they did this?

258
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,200
Could it be

259
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,450
they don't know it themselves?

260
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:42,490
So if it's like you said,

261
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:44,850
there's really someone behind this case,

262
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:46,260
why do you think

263
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:47,480
he did this?

264
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,410
It's a provocation,

265
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:50,980
and a declaration.

266
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,380
Telling us he's always been here.

267
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:56,680
He's just like the Scavenger back then,

268
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,520
extremely arrogant.

269
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:00,850
Confident we'll never track him down.

270
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:04,440
I already shot the Scavenger back then.

271
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:04,800
Ah.

272
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:06,280
This is at most

273
00:14:06,280 --> 00:14:07,000
a copycat.

274
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,760
My dad must have told you,

275
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,660
never underestimate your opponent.

276
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:17,620
Then why did he reappear as soon as you showed up?

277
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:20,540
Does he consider you an opponent?

278
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,940
Why don't you call me a scavenger?

279
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:26,020
I was just joking with you.

280
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:28,800
Very funny.

281
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:31,730
Alright.

282
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:33,160
Stop worrying about it.

283
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:34,890
I'll handle it if the sky falls.

284
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:37,600
You'd probably eat first even if the sky falls.

285
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,120
Hey.

286
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:41,140
You're getting to know me better.

287
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:43,980
I saw your medical report.

288
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:46,360
You have secondary gastroparesis.

289
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:49,160
Thank you

290
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:50,760
for taking a knife for my dad.

291
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,880
Master, your medical report

292
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:56,280
was just left on the desk.

293
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:07,560
Your favorite West Lake fish in vinegar gravy.

294
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,320
Thank you,

295
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:09,410
Auntie Rong.

296
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:11,800
Eat up.

297
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:20,860
The case is solved.

298
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,660
Then why aren't you happy?

299
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:31,560
Technically,

300
00:15:32,280 --> 00:15:34,560
I shouldn't share the case details with you.

301
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:36,360
But being led by the nose

302
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,760
feels absolutely awful.

303
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,480
I suspect

304
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:44,240
that behind these three women,

305
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,770
there must be someone else.

306
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:49,620
But right now there is no evidence at all.

307
00:15:51,160 --> 00:15:52,080
Don't worry.

308
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,960
You're so smart.

309
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:56,820
Solving the case is only a matter of time.

310
00:15:57,880 --> 00:15:58,810
Hurry up and eat.

311
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:25,970
There are symbols here.

312
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:30,180
Look at these symbols.

313
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,400
They look like Nushu.

314
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,200
Women of the world

315
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:47,240
are sisters.

316
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,930
So you told me the answer from the very beginning.

317
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:04,730
Working overtime instead of resting?

318
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:06,800
Why don't you make a sound when you walk?

319
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:07,599
You scared me.

320
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:09,400
What are you looking at?

321
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,460
There is a new clue.

322
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:12,800
Look.

323
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:13,940
Right here.

324
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:20,000
What is written here?

325
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:20,849
Look at this.

326
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,760
This is a type of script called

327
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:25,359
Nüshu.

328
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:28,280
It's a script used exclusively by women.

329
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:30,440
It originated in

330
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:32,160
Jiangyong, Hunan.

331
00:17:33,080 --> 00:17:34,360
These four characters mean

332
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:35,560
'Women of the world.'

333
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:36,620
And over there,

334
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:38,120
'Sisters as one family.'

335
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:40,960
I still can't understand it.

336
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,060
What's the point of this clue?

337
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:46,600
Besides, the case has already been handed over to the procuratorate.

338
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:48,120
Then apply to the procuratorate to return it

339
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:49,200
for further investigation.

340
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,360
We have to interrogate Qi Xiaoling and the others again.

341
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:52,820
You still insist this case

342
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:53,960
has someone else behind it?

343
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:54,490
Exactly.

344
00:17:54,800 --> 00:17:57,000
If even they don't know the secret on the paper figures,

345
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:59,060
there must be someone else behind it.

346
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:00,280
Fine.

347
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,970
You go tell Chief Zhang.

348
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,560
It has nothing to do with me.

349
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:04,280
Don't mention me.

350
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:05,120
I can't help.

351
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:07,640
Wait.

352
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:10,460
Are you the captain or am I?

353
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,480
This is the family.

354
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:18,200
The wife cheated on the husband.

355
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,360
The husband threatened suicide.

356
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:19,960
Who knew

357
00:18:19,960 --> 00:18:20,960
it would become real?

358
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:23,960
I heard the wife conspired with someone to kill her husband.

359
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:24,880
It's terrifying.
